longBusinessSummary: Green EnviroTech Holdings Corp. operates as a plastics recovery, separation, cleaning, and recycling company. The company transforms unusable scrap tires into various end products, such as carbon black, oil, and steel. It also offers Generation One, which produces a blend stock oil, char/carbon, and steel. The company was founded in 2008 and is based in Jamestown, California.
